During Gift Fest, all cash players on Gift Fest tables during the allocated times have a chance to win random cash and ticket prizes.
Gift boxes will contain a large variety of Cash and Ticket prizes. A spinner will appear to determine a player’s prize.
HOW CAN I FIND A GIFT FEST TABLE?
Keep an eye out for the purple gift box icon next to a cash table in the lobby - this means it is a Gift Fest table.
HOW WILL I KNOW IF GIFT FEST IS ACTIVE?

In the top right-hand corner of any gift fest cash table, you will see a gift box with a timer.

If the timer says ‘starts in’ before it, Gift Fest is not yet active on that table but will become active once the timer has ticked down.

If the timer is ticking down with no ‘starts in’ note, then the Gift Fest promotion is active and you can win a gift box at any time.
HOW WILL I KNOW IF I WIN A GIFT BOX?
If you win a Gift Box, a small gift box will appear on your table and you’ll be directed to click the countdown icon to open your box. A spinner will then appear to determine your prize.
